---
title: HelloHero: Coconut Halloumi & Veg Curry with Baby Leaves & Flatbreads
description: Enjoy this sunset in a bowl, the glowing curry is brimming with veggies and halloumi. The hint of coconut gives it a touch of sunny flavour and you can soak it all up with fluffy flatbreads, perfect for dipping.

